---
title: Sweet Soy-Glazed Salmon & Kale Salad with Cabbage, Pickled Veggies & Peanuts
description: Get ready for a fish dish that’s light, filling, flavorful, and on the table in a quick and easy 15 minutes! You’ll drizzle seared salmon with a sweet soy glaze, and serve it over sesame-dressed kale and cabbage salad topped with tangy pickled red onion and carrots and sprinkled with crunchy peanuts. The only question is: What will you do with all that time you freed up by picking this meal?
